5 health literacy of their patients to improve the patient’s ability to obtain, process, and
6 understand basic health information and services to make appropriate health care
7 decisions;
8 (2) Establish and provide an evidence–based implicit bias training
9 program for health care professionals involved in the perinatal care of patients under §
10 20–1305 of this subtitle; and
11 (3) Identify and approve implicit bias AND STRUCTURAL RACISM training
12 programs for health occupation licensure and certification under § 1–225 of the Health
